HA393E1888F8B486682695FAE869224AF.text: This Act may be cited as the “TANF Extension Act of 2019”.
HA393E1888F8B486682695FAE869224AF.author: jwagner

HC3AD2B9D5346491C8670924F31ED46F2.text: Activities authorized by part A of title IV and section 1108(b) of the Social Security Act shall continue through June 30, 2019, in the manner authorized for fiscal year 2018, and out of any money in the Treasury of the United States not otherwise appropriated, there are hereby appropriated such sums as may be necessary for such purpose.
